enough to do it.

22:33.485 --> 22:40.192 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MYSONE MAHANE: We don't support
killing, not for Jews, not for
any -- for Israelis. We

22:40.192 --> 22:45.531 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
don't support this, of course,
especially the honest people,
the innocent people,
Palestinians

22:45.531 --> 22:48.300 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
or Israelis. We
don't support this.

22:48.300 --> 22:51.203 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARTIN SEEMUNGAL: Even Elbazi,
one of the Israeli witnesses to
the attack, is finding

22:51.203 --> 22:55.140 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
it difficult to comprehend, but
