22:55.140 --> 23:01.647 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
EYAL ELBAZI: I think 13 year old
doesn't know what to think. I
don't think his father knew.

23:01.647 --> 23:06.385 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I don't think his mother knew. I
don't think the family knew
about it. I think he did it

23:06.385 --> 23:10.689 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
from Facebook or
something like that.

23:10.689 --> 23:16.061 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I don't think his dad will
approve something like that. Any
dad wouldn't approve his son

23:16.061 --> 23:21.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
