23:22.935 --> 23:26.639 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARTIN SEEMUNGAL: All of this is
playing out amid a surge of
violence between Palestinians

23:26.639 --> 23:33.045 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
