come to Beit Hanina because they
are afraid of being attacked.

24:04.810 --> 24:08.647 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But there is mistrust
and fear on both sides.

24:08.647 --> 24:14.586 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Has it changed attitudes of you
and your classmates towards
Israelis?

24:14.586 --> 24:20.759 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MOHAMMED, Palestinian: We hate
them, yes. They're bad people.
They kill Palestinians.

24:20.759 --> 24:24.163 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MARTIN SEEMUNGAL:
Fifteen-year-old Mohammed, also
from Beit Hanina and a close
friend of

24:24.163 --> 24:29.034 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Ahmed's now deceased cousin,
