video.

24:29.034 --> 24:34.707 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MOHAMMED: He was laying down. He
got up. He was -- a lot of
blood, but they were looking

24:34.707 --> 24:41.447 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
