him. They were not helping him.
That felt so bad.

24:41.447 --> 24:45.784 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARTIN SEEMUNGAL: Speaking to
young people from both sides of
this divide, it was hard

24:45.784 --> 24:49.855 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
